						<div class="postbody">I don't know but it would most certainly help to get used to harmony thing with 4 parts even if you plan to only use 3.
<br />(You could always use the FDS channel for one more part if you're only releasing NSFs.)
<br />
<br />I haven't composed any music for a long while (hell I should do that again how I'll forget how to do it) but I'm one of those guys for who less voices is a good thing. I've never managed to compose for many voices personally, but for some other people, it might be the other way around where the more voice there is the better.</div>

					
